(227, 84, 2, '1e38baf0-264b-4004-ba0a-5a346d460030', 'user', '10月のTP1無線パスワードが記載された通達を表示してください', '10月のTP1無線パスワードが記載された通達を表示してください', 'The notification about the change of the wireless LAN (TP-1) password for October 2023 is as follows:\n\nSSID: TP-1\nPassword: C-dMg6me\n\nPlease note that the TP-1 wireless LAN password will be changed at some point between 18:00 and 20:00 on the last day of the month due to service circumstances. If you cannot connect early in the evening, please try changing to the next month\'s password.\n\nFor the wireless LAN password update procedure, you can refer to this link: [https://crew.3pg.jp/scripts/cbag/ag.exe?page=FileIndex&gid=417&fCID=374212](https://crew.3pg.jp/scripts/cbag/ag.exe?page=FileIndex&gid=417&fCID=374212)', '2023-10-19 01:54:54', '2023-10-19 01:54:54', 0, '\n> 仮想【お知らせ】 Webページおよび無線LAN（TP-1）パスワード変更のご案内（2023年10月分）\n> テクニカルソリューション統括_PC相談内容', NULL),
